precis:
Enactment of the SPECIFIED CROWN AGENTS (GST) REGULATIONS which, for the
purposes of the definition "specified Crown agent" in subsection 123(1)
of the Excise Tax Act, prescribe the federal Crown agents who are excluded
from the general GST and HST exemption bestowed on government agencies.
